  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] And I remember also some people who lived in Hungary, but their ancestors came from Galicia, were expelled.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had expulsion orders.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they couldn't even speak another language, only Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were expelled and taken to the border, and, and let them go over the border, even a couple of shots in the air to make them run faster.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The other side was already occupied by Germany, so what happened to them--",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we knew, but see, I was a more or less [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had access to a shortwave radio.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Radios were-- shortwave radios who were held by Jewish people had to be sealed in the back and set to-- only to the Hungarian government station.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you couldn't have the dial moving.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- so they couldn't listen in to London or Moscow during the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They, they come and check you occasionally.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then you could get six months' imprisonment for not sealing your radio onto the one station.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what happens frequently, when I went on the summer holiday home to our village, no one had a radio in- in the village.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was only one official who had a radio, a Hungarian man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was operating on batteries, car batteries.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I went to Szilagy-Somlyo that 18 kilometers away, on a pushbike.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Took me about three quarters of an hour to an hour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had to memorize the news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the community in the synagogue, where I had to come back and tell the news.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
